# ============================================================
# Business / strategy documents — NEVER commit these.
# The outreach target list, pricing plans and day-one plan are worth more to a
# competitor than the source code is. They were public for 49 commits because
# of `git add .`.
#
# Everything in Business/ is invisible to git — even `git add .` cannot stage it.
# Put every plan, deck, target list and contact sheet in there. If a document is
# about the COMPANY rather than the CODE, it belongs in Business/.
# ============================================================
Business/

